\f0\b\fs32 \cf0 How the List Relates to the \'93Hard Problem\'94\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f3\b0\fs18 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs26 Each entry poses its own explanatory gap: 
\f0\b Why does a particular neural configuration give rise to the qualia of red?
\f1\b0  (visual consciousness) versus 
\f0\b Why does a recurrent loop produce the feeling of \'93I am thinking\'94?
\f1\b0  (meta\uc0\u8209 consciousness).\
\ls5\ilvl0
\f3\fs18 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f1\fs26 The \'93hard problem\'94 originally highlighted the gap for 
\f0\b phenomenal consciousness
\f1\b0  in general, but once we recognize that many distinct phenomenological and functional varieties exist, we end up with a family of hard problems\'97one for each form.\
